Title: First Documents Article for 10th Anniversary Newsletter
Description.note: Rights.statementLocal: Not sure if copyright is held by organization or by individual author.|~|Details the origins of SCWU as a "support group" of the Whitman-Radclyffe Foundation (WRF). MacCulloch briefly outlines SCWU's initial challenges and learning process of working together, by-law and policy-making, official severance from WRF, estrangement from original members Terry DeCrescenzo and Betty Berzon, and the resignation/firing of June Mazer as newsletter co-editor.
